title: GraphicRiver - Smudge Art Photoshop Action
description:
Create stunning contemporary brushed artwork from any photo.
Its super easy to use and save yourself hours of work. Final composition is fully layered. Lots of effects and customization. Duplicate layers and create more effects.
10+10 color presets are also included.
Tweak settings to match your style.
Mix different styles to create your own stunning composition. Please go through the video guide on how to load up the action and customize the effects.

Tested and assured Tested with more than 50 images to assure the integrity of the action.

Recommended size The action works best with images having size around 2500-3500px and 72-300dpi. Using lower resolution images will result in lower details and clarity of the final composition.

The action will only work in the English version of the Photoshop. 

Package: 1 Photoshop atn action file
1 Photoshop abr brush file
1 Photoshop pat pattern file
